title: The Sinister Six put Spider-Man in a Coma
description:
Spider-Man faces off against his greatest foe; math.

I’m sorry if the audio isn’t that good, away from home so this had to be done in the shoddiest way imaginable. No mic, no equipment, just a man and the voices in his head. And 1 gold coin.
